title: Rhubarb
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Japanese, Organic, Western
description: Part of an organic wholefoods store. Food is mostly vegan except for options of dairy milk, yogurt and honey. Large space with vintage chic decor. Serves lunch/brunch food with a slight Japanese influence. Serves Streat coffee, which is organic, fairtrade and donates to support homeless people. Cafe has both regular Western-style tables and chairs, and low Japanese-style tables.
